WHY DOES IT HURT
SO MUCH?

00:00:24.798 --> 00:00:27.234
I CAN'T REMEMBER.

00:00:27.234 --> 00:00:29.603
LEMME TELL YA
HOW THINGS ARE GONNA
WORK AROUND HERE.

