'CAUSE I'M THE BEST.

00:00:37.811 --> 00:00:40.480
OOOOOOKAY! LET'S
EVERYONE CALM DOWN!

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:41.648
I'VE BEEN
HERE BEFORE

00:00:41.648 --> 00:00:42.816
AND I KNOW HOW
THE RULES

00:00:42.816 --> 00:00:43.850
ARE SUPPOSED
TO WORK!

00:00:43.884 --> 00:00:46.586
IF I WIN, THEN
WELL I'M IN CHARGE.

00:00:46.586 --> 00:00:49.956
USHI ONI, TAKE OUT
THAT ANCIENT RELIC!

00:00:49.956 --> 00:00:51.391
YOU CAN'T!

00:00:51.391 --> 00:00:54.928
THE CRYSTAL SKULL IS
A PRICELESS ARTIFACT!

00:00:54.928 --> 00:00:57.631
AAH!

00:00:57.631 --> 00:00:59.166
NOW GET OUTTA HERE.

00:00:59.166 --> 00:01:01.568
AND LEAVE YOUR
"PRECIOUS TREASURES"
WITH ME!

00:01:01.568 --> 00:01:05.439
YOU CAN'T DO THIS!

00:01:05.439 --> 00:01:07.774
[GROANING]

00:01:10.944 --> 00:01:13.980
LOOKS LIKE YOU JUST
EARNED YOURSELF A DUEL!

00:01:13.980 --> 00:01:15.215
CAN I BORROW
YOUR CARDS?

00:01:15.215 --> 00:01:16.450
HUH?

00:01:16.450 --> 00:01:18.185
YOU SAID WE DUEL
HERE FOR RESPECT.

00:01:18.185 --> 00:01:19.719
I THINK IT'S ABOUT
TIME YOU LEARN

00:01:19.719 --> 00:01:21.588
WHAT THAT REALLY MEANS.

00:01:21.588 --> 00:01:23.256
THIS STARTED TO BURN!

00:01:23.256 --> 00:01:25.158
IT'S THE CRIMSON
DRAGON'S MARK.

00:01:25.158 --> 00:01:26.493
IT'S A SYMBOL
OF POWER.

00:01:26.493 --> 00:01:28.862
YOU ARE ONE
OF THE RARE FEW
KNOWN AS A SIGNER.

00:01:28.862 --> 00:01:31.465
YOUR SIGN, JACK,
IT IS YOUR DESTINY.

