THERE'S NOW WAY YOU
GOT THE SKILLS TO
TAKE ME DOWN.

00:02:38.899 --> 00:02:41.401
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE GETTIN'
INTO, KID?

00:02:41.401 --> 00:02:44.571
BRING IT ON
AND FIND OUT.

00:02:44.571 --> 00:02:47.874
WELL AT LEAST YOU GOT
THE WHOLE ATTITUDE
THING COVERED.

00:02:47.874 --> 00:02:49.709
YOU'RE GONNA DUEL
WITH THE OLD GUY'S
DECK?

00:02:49.709 --> 00:02:51.144
GUESS YOUR LOOKING
TO GET EMBARRASSED

00:02:51.144 --> 00:02:52.812
BY TANNER AS WELL!

00:02:52.812 --> 00:02:55.048
THEY ARE BUNKMATES,
MAYBE CRAZY'S CONTAGIOUS.

00:02:55.048 --> 00:02:57.450
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
DO THIS, YOU KNOW.

00:02:57.450 --> 00:03:01.054
IF I DON'T STEP UP,
I'LL NEVER LIVE IT DOWN.

00:03:01.054 --> 00:03:02.722
[THINKING]
THERE'S SOMETHING
SPECIAL ABOUT

00:03:02.722 --> 00:03:04.324
THIS WHIPPER-SNAPPER.

00:03:04.324 --> 00:03:06.526
IF I REALLY SAW
WHAT I THINK I SAW

00:03:06.526 --> 00:03:08.428
THE OTHER NIGHT,
IS IT POSSIBLE

00:03:08.428 --> 00:03:12.032
THAT THIS KID IS
WHO I THINK HE IS?

00:03:12.032 --> 00:03:13.833
WHO ARE YOU?

00:03:13.833 --> 00:03:16.469
JUST A GUY
TRYING TO GET BY.

00:03:16.469 --> 00:03:18.305
YOU LOSE A DUEL
IN HERE, ROOKIE,

00:03:18.305 --> 00:03:20.106
AND NO ONE'S
GONNA RESPECT YOU.

00:03:20.106 --> 00:03:22.175
AND TRUST ME...
AROUND HERE,

00:03:22.175 --> 00:03:23.910
YOU SURVIVE ON RESPECT.

00:03:23.910 --> 00:03:27.614
WELL, THEN YOU BETTER
HOPE YOU DON'T LOSE.

00:03:27.614 --> 00:03:28.915
LET'S DO THIS!

00:03:30.250 --> 00:03:32.052
SENIORITY RULES HERE!

00:03:32.052 --> 00:03:33.420
I'M GOIN' FIRST!

00:03:35.388 --> 00:03:37.324
LEMME INTRODUCE YOU
TO MY LITTLE PET!

00:03:37.324 --> 00:03:38.858
JIRAI GUMO!

00:03:40.694 --> 00:03:42.862
YARGHHH! SPIDER!!!!

00:03:42.862 --> 00:03:44.197
WHAT'S WRONG,
GRAMPS!?

00:03:44.197 --> 00:03:46.766
CREEPIE CRAWLIES
GIVING YA
THE SHAKES?

00:03:46.766 --> 00:03:48.301
COME ON, TANNER!
GET 'EM!

00:03:48.301 --> 00:03:50.370
YEAH! GO!

00:03:50.370 --> 00:03:52.305
COME ON, MAN!

00:03:52.305 --> 00:03:53.940
YOU CAN DO IT.
COME ON!

00:03:53.940 --> 00:03:57.344
I PLACE TWO
CARDS FACEDOWN
AND END MY TURN!

00:03:57.344 --> 00:03:59.613
IT'S YOUR MOVE, KID.

00:03:59.613 --> 00:04:01.748
HOW'S THE OLD TIMER'S
DECK LOOKIN'?

00:04:01.748 --> 00:04:05.552
YOU GONNA THROW
SOME GARAGE SALE
REJECTS AT ME?

00:04:05.552 --> 00:04:08.688
HEY, YANAGI, DON'T LISTEN
TO ANYTHING

00:04:08.688 --> 00:04:10.624
THESE GUYS HAVE TO SAY.

00:04:10.624 --> 00:04:12.359
THEY DON'T KNOW WHAT
THEY'RE TALKING ABOUT.

00:04:12.359 --> 00:04:14.094
BUT YOU SAW ME DUEL.

00:04:14.094 --> 00:04:16.263
EVERYTHING BLEW
UP IN MY FACE.

00:04:16.263 --> 00:04:19.099
I HAD MY OLD BUTT
HANDED TO ME.

00:04:19.099 --> 00:04:20.367
WELL, LET ME SHOW YOU
WHAT THESE

00:04:20.367 --> 00:04:23.336
ANCIENT RELICS OF YOURS
CAN DO IN THE RIGHT HANDS.

00:04:27.907 --> 00:04:29.776
[TELEPHONE DIALING]

00:04:31.444 --> 00:04:34.247
Goodwin: YES UNDERSTOOD.
JUST BE SURE TO KEEP AN EYE

00:04:34.247 --> 00:04:36.449
ON THAT DUEL,
MR. ARMSTRONG.

00:04:36.449 --> 00:04:38.118
WRITE UP A REPORT.

00:04:38.118 --> 00:04:42.022
BE SURE TO NOTE
IF ANYTHING
UNUSUAL HAPPENS.

00:04:42.022 --> 00:04:43.957
SOUNDS LIKE YOUR OLD
BUDDY FROM THE SATELLITE

00:04:43.957 --> 00:04:45.592
IS MAKING SOME
NEW DUELIST FRIENDS

00:04:45.592 --> 00:04:47.127
IN THE FACILITY.

00:04:47.127 --> 00:04:49.696
HUH!

00:04:49.696 --> 00:04:52.332
LOOK, JACK, I'M SORRY
ABOUT HOW RECENT EVENTS

00:04:52.332 --> 00:04:53.633
HAVE TRANSPIRED.

00:04:53.633 --> 00:04:56.002
BUT ALLOW ME
TO EXPLAIN.

00:04:56.002 --> 00:04:57.337
SO FAR, OUR
RELATIONSHIP
HAS OPERATED

00:04:57.337 --> 00:04:59.039
ON A NEED-TO-KNOW
BASIS.

00:04:59.039 --> 00:05:01.574
MEANING I KNOW
THINGS THAT YOU DON'T.

00:05:01.574 --> 00:05:04.311
'CAUSE YOU
HAVEN'T NEEDED
TO KNOW THESE THINGS.

00:05:04.311 --> 00:05:05.645
UNTIL NOW.

00:05:09.115 --> 00:05:11.184
Computer:
FINGERPRINT VERIFICATION.

00:05:11.184 --> 00:05:14.020
OPTICAL ANALYSIS.

00:05:14.020 --> 00:05:15.755
SCAN COMPLETE.

00:05:15.755 --> 00:05:17.223
WELCOME, MR. GOODWIN.

00:05:24.964 --> 00:05:27.567
YOU'RE A LOT MORE
IMPORTANT THAN
YOU KNOW, JACK.

00:05:27.567 --> 00:05:31.504
BUT WHAT MAKES YOU
IMPORTANT IS NOT THAT
YOU'RE A GREAT DUELIST.

00:05:31.504 --> 00:05:34.774
RATHER YOU'RE A GREAT
DUELIST BECAUSE OF WHAT
MAKES YOU IMPORTANT.

00:05:34.774 --> 00:05:37.110
I'M GONNA PRETEND
THAT MADE SENSE.

00:05:37.110 --> 00:05:39.679
BEYOND THIS DOOR
LIES YOUR DESTINY.

00:05:48.621 --> 00:05:51.958
WHAT'S GOING ON,
GOODWIN?

00:05:51.958 --> 00:05:53.526
WHAT I'M ABOUT TO
SHOW YOU IS ONE

00:05:53.526 --> 00:05:56.529
OF THE WORLD'S
BEST KEPT SECRETS.

00:05:56.529 --> 00:06:00.633
AMAZING ISN'T IT?

00:06:00.633 --> 00:06:03.169
HEY! THAT DRAGON SYMBOL
LOOKS LIKE...

00:06:05.772 --> 00:06:08.141
NOW LISTEN CLOSELY, JACK.
YOU'RE STANDING IN FRONT

00:06:08.141 --> 00:06:10.877
OF THE STAIRWAY
OF THE CRIMSON DRAGON.

00:06:10.877 --> 00:06:12.645
IT WAS ORIGINALLY
ERECTED IN PERU,

00:06:12.645 --> 00:06:15.615
BUT MY PREDECESSORS
RELOCATED IT HERE

00:06:15.615 --> 00:06:18.985
THAT'S ALL WELL AND GOOD,
BUT HOW DOES THAT
RELATE TO THIS MARK?

00:06:18.985 --> 00:06:20.920
THE MARK ON YOUR ARM
REPRESENTS
THE RIGHT WING

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:22.655
OF THE CRIMSON DRAGON.

00:06:22.655 --> 00:06:24.791
THE SAME DRAGON YOU
AND YUSEI SOMEHOW
SUMMONED

00:06:24.791 --> 00:06:26.459
AT THE END OF YOUR DUEL.

00:06:26.459 --> 00:06:29.963
LIKE I SAID, JACK,
YOU'RE MUCH MORE
IMPORTANT THAN YOU KNOW.

00:06:44.793 --> 00:06:48.297
MY MOVE, TANNER.

00:06:48.297 --> 00:06:50.065
[THINKING]
THIS WON'T HELP NOW.

00:06:50.065 --> 00:06:53.102
UH, WHATEVER YOU DO,
DON'T USE
THE CRYSTAL SKULL!

00:06:53.135 --> 00:06:55.804
THE CRYSTAL SKULL.
GOOD IDEA!

00:06:55.804 --> 00:06:58.007
WHAT ARE YOU...
I SAID DON'T USE IT,

00:06:58.007 --> 00:07:00.209
DIDN'T YOU SEE
WHAT IT DID TO ME?!

00:07:00.209 --> 00:07:02.778
I SUMMON CRYSTAL SKULL
IN DEFENSE MODE!

00:07:09.518 --> 00:07:12.321
YOU CAN'T SAY I
DIDN'T WARN YOU.

00:07:14.423 --> 00:07:16.091
YOU KNOW THAT
SKULL'S CURSED.

00:07:16.125 --> 00:07:18.460
WHY PLAY SOMETHING
THAT ATTACKS YOURSELF?

00:07:18.460 --> 00:07:21.897
GOOD QUESTION.
WHY WOULD I?

00:07:21.897 --> 00:07:23.265
IT'D BE
A STUPID MOVE.

00:07:23.265 --> 00:07:25.534
UNLESS OF COURSE
I HAD THIS!

00:07:25.534 --> 00:07:27.803
OH I REMEMBER
THAT ONE!

00:07:27.803 --> 00:07:30.539
I GOT THAT FROM
A FRIENDLY SHAMAN
IN AFRICA,

00:07:30.539 --> 00:07:32.041
BUT HE NEVER GOT
THE CHANCE

00:07:32.041 --> 00:07:34.009
TO EXPLAIN
HOW IT WORKED.

00:07:39.748 --> 00:07:41.150
WHAT'S GOIN ON!?

00:07:48.991 --> 00:07:50.759
WHAT JUST HAPPENED?

00:07:50.759 --> 00:07:53.028
SEEMS EVERYTHING PLAYED
OUT ALL OPPOSITE-LIKE.

00:07:53.028 --> 00:07:55.964
TANNER ENDED UP LOSING
A THOUSAND LIFE POINTS.

00:07:55.964 --> 00:07:58.600
AND THE NEW GUY DIDN'T
TAKE ANY DAMAGE AT ALL.

00:07:58.600 --> 00:08:01.437
HOW'D YOU DO THAT?
WHAT WAS THAT CARD
YOU JUST PLAYED?

00:08:01.437 --> 00:08:03.272
THE CURSE REFLECTION DOLL.

00:08:03.272 --> 00:08:05.541
NORMALLY IT'S USED TO
REFLECT CURSE ATTACKS

00:08:05.541 --> 00:08:07.543
SENT BY THE OPPONENT,
BUT IM GONNA USE IT

00:08:07.543 --> 00:08:10.813
TO TURN MY OWN CURSE
INTO AN ATTACK AGAINST YOU.

00:08:10.813 --> 00:08:13.682
SO THE NEWBIE FOUND
SOME CRAZY CLEVER WAY

00:08:13.682 --> 00:08:15.350
TO PUT THAT CURSE
IN REVERSE!

00:08:15.350 --> 00:08:18.320
I'M JUST SO GLAD
THAT SOMEONE
OTHER THAN ME

00:08:18.320 --> 00:08:20.889
CAN SEE
THE TRUE VALUE
OF THESE CARDS.

00:08:20.889 --> 00:08:23.292
WELL, I NEVER MET
A CARD I DIDN'T LIKE.

00:08:23.292 --> 00:08:24.359
HUH?

00:08:24.359 --> 00:08:25.794
YOU SEE EVERY CARD
IS SPECIAL,

00:08:25.794 --> 00:08:28.330
AND YOU JUST HAVE TO LEARN
TO APPRECIATE ITS POWER

00:08:28.330 --> 00:08:31.100
IN ORDER TO FIGURE OUT
HOW TO BEST USE IT.

00:08:31.133 --> 00:08:33.502
SO YOU DON'T THINK
THEY'RE WORTHLESS?

00:08:33.502 --> 00:08:36.972
NO WAY, THIS DECK
IS INCREDIBLE.

00:08:36.972 --> 00:08:40.843
I KNEW IT I
JUST KNEW IT.

00:08:40.843 --> 00:08:42.845
HEY COME ON,
DON'T SWEAT IT, TANNER!

00:08:42.845 --> 00:08:44.780
THE NEW KID JUST GOT
LUCKY IS ALL.

00:08:44.780 --> 00:08:46.081
DON'T YOU LET IT
GET TO YA'!

00:08:46.081 --> 00:08:49.284
NO. THAT WAS NOT LUCK.

00:08:49.284 --> 00:08:51.620
IF THE PRO DUELS
TAUGHT ME ONE THING

00:08:51.620 --> 00:08:54.223
IT WAS HOW TO SPOT
A GOOD OPPONENT.

00:08:54.223 --> 00:08:56.058
AND SOMETHIN' TELLS ME
THIS NEWBIE MAY ACTUALLY

00:08:56.058 --> 00:08:57.860
KNOW WHAT HE'S DOIN'.

00:08:57.860 --> 00:08:59.328
IT'S YOUR MOVE,
TANNER.

00:08:59.328 --> 00:09:01.964
HEY, YOU GUYS,
WAS TANNER ACTUALLY

00:09:01.964 --> 00:09:03.298
BEIN' NICE FOR ONCE?

00:09:03.298 --> 00:09:06.168
IT'S MY TURN.
I DRAW!

00:09:06.168 --> 00:09:08.437
SWEET!

00:09:08.437 --> 00:09:10.606
I RELEASE JIRAI GUMO

00:09:10.606 --> 00:09:14.143
IN ORDER TO SUMMON
USHI ONI!

00:09:14.143 --> 00:09:16.478
NOW WHY WOULD
HE DO THAT?

00:09:16.478 --> 00:09:19.414
JIRAI GUMO IS
MORE POWERFUL THAN
THIS MONSTER.

00:09:19.414 --> 00:09:21.016
JUST WAIT, OLD TIMER.

00:09:21.016 --> 00:09:22.718
THE REAL SHOW'S
ABOUT TO BEGIN!

00:09:22.718 --> 00:09:25.387
NOW, I RELEASE
USHI ONI TO SUMMON

00:09:25.387 --> 00:09:27.322
GIANT USHI ONI!

00:09:30.626 --> 00:09:33.028
AND NEXT MY GIANT
USHI ONI'S TAKING OUT

00:09:33.028 --> 00:09:35.531
YOUR CRYSTAL SKULL!

00:09:35.531 --> 00:09:36.899
YEAH, CRACK UP
THAT CRYSTAL!

00:09:36.899 --> 00:09:37.900
OH YEAH!!

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:40.169
[WHIMPERS]

00:09:40.169 --> 00:09:41.703
GO SPECTRE'S BITE!

00:09:44.273 --> 00:09:45.274
AAH!

00:09:48.477 --> 00:09:49.912
THAT WAS ONLY
THE BEGINNING

00:09:49.912 --> 00:09:51.213
OF YOUR WORRIES.

00:09:51.213 --> 00:09:53.682
'CAUSE WHEN GIANT USHI ONI
DESTROYS A MONSTER

00:09:53.682 --> 00:09:56.218
IN BATTLE,
IT GETS TO ATTACK AGAIN!

00:09:56.218 --> 00:09:58.754
AND WITH CRYSTAL SKULL
GONE, YOU'VE GOT

00:09:58.754 --> 00:10:02.457
NO DEFENSE, SO YOU'RE OPEN
FOR A DIRECT ATTACK!

00:10:02.457 --> 00:10:03.926
YOU'RE REALLY GETTING
CAUGHT UP IN THIS DUEL,

00:10:03.926 --> 00:10:05.227
AREN'T YA?!

00:10:05.227 --> 00:10:06.261
YOU OKAY?

00:10:06.261 --> 00:10:07.763
THAT WAS AWESOME.

00:10:07.763 --> 00:10:09.898
THIS GUY JUST AIN'T
GOT WHAT IT TAKES.

00:10:09.898 --> 00:10:12.768
SO ARE YOU ANY
GOOD AT ALL, KID?

00:10:12.768 --> 00:10:15.504
OR ARE YOU THE LOSER
THESE GUYS SAY YOU ARE?!

00:10:32.592 --> 00:10:33.927
Goodwin: JACK, ALLOW ME
TO SHED SOME LIGHT.

00:10:33.927 --> 00:10:36.930
I AM THE 360th
GUARDIAN OF THE STAR.

00:10:36.930 --> 00:10:39.299
THROUGHOUT HISTORY,
MY ORDER HAS BEEN KNOWN
BY MANY NAMES...

00:10:39.299 --> 00:10:42.502
THE DEFENDERS OF PEACE,
THE SERVANTS TO THE STARS.

00:10:42.502 --> 00:10:44.237
WE HAVE SWORN
TO MAINTAIN BALANCE

00:10:44.237 --> 00:10:48.008
IN THE UNIVERSE BY TAKING
THE OATH OF ILIASTER.

00:10:48.008 --> 00:10:50.377
THE WHAT NOW?

00:10:50.377 --> 00:10:52.112
IT IS THE POWER
THAT GIVES EVERYTHING

00:10:52.112 --> 00:10:53.680
IN NATURE ITS
INNER ESSENCE

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:55.449
AND OUTWARD FORM...

00:10:55.449 --> 00:10:58.251
THE UNIVERSE, ENERGY,
MANKIND.

00:10:58.251 --> 00:10:59.920
ILIASTER IS
THE POWER FLOWING

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:02.155
THROUGH ALL OF THESE THINGS,
BINDING THEM TOGETHER.

00:11:02.155 --> 00:11:03.457
SO IT'S GLUE.

00:11:03.457 --> 00:11:05.992
YOU'VE SWORN ALLEGIANCE
TO MAGIC GLUE.

00:11:05.992 --> 00:11:08.328
JOKE ALL YOU WANT,
BUT THAT MARK ON YOUR ARM?

00:11:08.328 --> 00:11:10.931
IT MEANS YOU'RE PART
OF SOMETHING MUCH GREATER,

00:11:10.931 --> 00:11:13.333
AND IF YOUR FRIEND YUSEI
REALLY DOES HAVE A MARK,

00:11:13.333 --> 00:11:14.901
THEN HE'S PART
OF IT, TOO.

00:11:16.737 --> 00:11:19.406
FROM MY HAND
I SUMMON ASHOKA PILLAR

00:11:19.406 --> 00:11:20.907
IN DEFENSE MODE!

